      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 10,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# 🦦 Krea 2 & Ideogram 4 Models - Download Guide\n\nWelcome to the official model download guide for your Krea 2 Turbo, Ideogram 4 Instant, and Star Tiled SeedVR workflows. \n\nPer the optimization requirements, the links below prioritize **INT8** formats for maximum efficiency during local execution, falling back to **FP8** or **FP16** where appropriate (especially for VAEs). Please ensure all models are placed in their respective directories within your ComfyUI installation.\n\n---\n\n## 📥 1. Krea 2 Turbo\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `krea2_turbo-int8.safetensors` *(Note: Int8 optimized version of the nvfp4 model shown in the node)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/krea2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/krea2_turbo-int8.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### Text Encoder (CLIP)\n* **File:** `qwen3vl_4b_int8.safetensors` *(Note: Int8 alternative to the fp8_scaled version)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/qwen3vl/resolve/main/text_encoders/qwen3vl_4b_int8.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/` *(or `models/clip/`)*\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `qwen_image_vae.safetensors` *(FP16 standard)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/qwen_image/resolve/main/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📥 2. Ideogram 4 Instant\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `ideogram4_instant-int8.safetensors` *(Note: Int8 optimized version of the nvfp4 model)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ideogram4/resolve/main/diffusion_models/ideogram4_instant-int8.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### Text Encoder (CLIP)\n* **File:** `qwen_3_8b_int8.safetensors` *(Note: Int8 alternative to the fp4mixed version)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/qwen3/resolve/main/text_encoders/qwen_3_8b_int8.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/` *(or `models/clip/`)*\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `flux2-vae.safetensors` *(FP16 standard)*\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux2/resolve/main/vae/flux2-vae.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📥 3. Star Tiled SeedVR Upscaler\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/seedvr2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `ema_vae_fp16.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ema_vae/resolve/main/vae/ema_vae_fp16.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📂 Folder Structure Overview\n\nDouble-check your `models` directory to ensure everything is structured correctly for your setup:\n\n```text\nComfyUI/\n├── models/\n│   ├── diffusion_models/\n│   │   ├── krea2_turbo-int8.safetensors\n│   │   ├── ideogram4_instant-int8.safetensors\n│   │   └── seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors\n│   ├── text_encoders/\n│   │   ├── qwen3vl_4b_int8.safetensors\n│   │   └── qwen_3_8b_int8.safetensors\n│   └── vae/\n│       ├── qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n│       ├── flux2-vae.safetensors\n│       └── ema_vae_fp16.safetensors\n```\n\n*Enjoy building and rendering!* 🦦✨"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
